Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Girl From America"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're awake, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}Oi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, I had some things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mokuba-kun, the seal has been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's my big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is my big brother at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Croquet-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master Pegasus has been sent away to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Bakura-kun can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}But the Millennium Ring was thrown away...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A card called the {\c&H00CAE2&}Bonds of Friendship{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master Pegasus told me to give this to Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys did well in your duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's great, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now Shizuka-chan can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka, wait for me... I'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi. The seal on Mokuba-kun was broken. Could it be....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fade(0,1200)}Grandpa must be.....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yu-gi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's Kaiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother.....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Geez. You have to take care of each other, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Brother, I protected our Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure they haven't discovered that this is the key card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mokuba, that was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You protected Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, you saved Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But Yugi, don't you forget that our duel is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm looking forward to dueling you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}It was thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}We did it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}No, not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,100)}It's everyone's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come to think of it, how are we going to get off this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah... hold on a minute, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't leave us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I finally got the Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome back, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see! Good job, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. Everyone helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, everyone. Especially me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright. Let's all celebrate tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa, the doctor said you need rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are ya talkin' about?! As you can see, I'm perfectly healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you sure you're alright gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's that? Someone we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You Suguroku Mutou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am. And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name is Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I arrived here this morning from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My goodness! You guys are so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the meaning of keeping a lady waiting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's that? Aren't I a lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oi oi, why are you coming all the way to Japan by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goddamn! I don't speak to impolite people like this guy. Right, Teddy-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What'd ya say? You punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, what did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give back the Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up and give it back! It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That card's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Blue-Eyes White Dragon was an American super rare card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's only right that I, America's number one strongest, should have it. Right, Teddy-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}America's number one strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right. Because I'm the U.S. Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U.S. Champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no mistake. I saw her on a magazine once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Winning the American Championship at the age of 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A genius duelist who had stirred up quite a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oi oi... This damn cocky girl is the U.S. Champion? Stop kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What! Are you insulting me, the U.S. Champion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut it! I won second place at the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right, right. Now risen from number 8 to number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You punk! Who's side are you on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know all that. The number one at Duelist Kingdom is Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And second place is Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyone who's not first place ain't important. Right, Teddy-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You jerk! Don't you look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, the Blue-Eyes White Dragon is an important card to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course it is! You stole it from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stole? Rebecca, there must be some misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm, Grandpa wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I was told by Bandit Keith that someone stole the Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That idiot. Why'd he say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, Blue-Eyes belongs to me, the U.S. Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? I get it. You don't want to return it, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a second! It's not I don't want to return it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I explain it? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then let's fight for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With a duel! A duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suguroku Mutou, if I win you have to return the {\c&H1FA1BC&}Blue-Eyes{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on! Would you give it a rest already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay. Let's head to the duel ring! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I beg you, Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no helping it. The duel rings are booked for 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There won't be a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now! Hurry and take me there. Let's go. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the duel ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get started, Suguroku Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold it! How long are you going to keep me, the U.S. Champion, waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, I'll be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa just got out of the hospital. He's not well enough to duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK! Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not too bad having the Duelist Kingdom first place Yugi Mutou as my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's impossible to defeat me, a genius duelist, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right, Teddy-chan~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell? How stuck up can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa, stay here and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Yugi. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey now, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, it's gonna be so easy. I'm the U.S. Champion after all. A genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right, Teddy-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes! Rebecca. A prodigy! Genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What does this little girl want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why does she want Blue-Eyes so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Witch of the Black Forest, Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Come out, my cute monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Witch of the Black Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Bandit Keith, and Pegasus J. Crawford...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I know something about American-styled duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How slow, Teddy-chan! What's taking him so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go. Elf Swordsman, Summon. Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Witch of the Black Forest is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOOO~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My Witch of the Black Forest was sent to the Graveyard~.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What now~?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When Witch of the Black Forest is sent to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A monster with 1500 Attack or less can be added to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then the deck is reshuffled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Teddy-chan! Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm thinking. Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she really the U.S. Champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, this one! Yeah, I'll play you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Critter, Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Critter, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, I'm going to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He defeated my Critter again and sent it to the Grave! Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You weren't going to win anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teddy-chan, that boy's taking advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What, I can't give up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Due to {\c&H134BBE&}Critter{\c&HFFFFFF&}'s effect, I get to take a monster from the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That girl's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this really a genius over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That damn brat!  I don't believe she's the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've seen that dueling style somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my turn now. Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The atmosphere just changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Magic Card, Welcome For the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It can destroy a monster by sacrificing a card in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Destroyed Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll put this card in standby Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's gonna get more interesting from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will get back the Blue-Eyes White Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't she different than a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's only 12, but she's still the U.S. Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like she's a totally different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I don't pay attention, I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn. Demon's Summon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You fell for it! This is Millennium Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's steel defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, Teddy-chan~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's not an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Millennium Shield, not bad, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, that's steel defense, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now then, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, Professor Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suguroku, why don't you call me Arthur from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just like that duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me for scaring you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:17:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a genius, so it's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, Teddy-chan. It's gonna get even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Magic Card, Ring of Magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ring of Magnetism?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This card can lower your Defense Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teddy-chan, it looks like he's completely clueless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll pass this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\pos(115,450)}Really? Are you\N gonna observe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cannon Soldier, Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cannon Soldier sacrifices a monster to attack the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's alright, gramps. Demon can block that weak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Demon's Summon, attack Cannon Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not a chance. Ring of Magnetism, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ring of Magnetism can absorb an attack from the enemy monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well? Now you can only attack Millennium Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not that easy to defeat a 2500 Defense monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Demon's Summon and Millennium Shield have the same Attack Points and Defense Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that doesn't mean it will be destroyed if it's in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teddy-chan, it's fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, it's my turn this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ha, I was waiting for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's not time to use it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I Summon Witch of the Black Forest in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I sacrifice Witch of the Black Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cannon Soldier, attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And use Witch of the Black Forest's effect to get a card from the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does that brat really have what it takes to be the U.S. number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll know the pain in your heart from losing the Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You finally found out. Yes, my name is Rebecca {\i1}Hopkins{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm {\i1}Arthur Hopkins{\i0}'s granddaughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the man you stole his cherished Blue-Eyes White Dragon from!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're Grandpa's best friend's granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right. Now! I'm going to avenge my grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That punk turns out to be Grandpa's best friend's granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi will clear his grandfather's name in this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, as we'd expect from the Whole Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rebecca is turning the match around with hard tactics, and making Yugi sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? This duel is the same as the one you played before, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then the ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On the next episode ''Deadly Shadow Ghoul''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:21:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:22:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
